    {
      "id": "PopularPost143006",
      "post_content": "...why did the change the flavour text? The [original version](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=5771) at least mentioned *why* the arrows were fletched like so. It improved accuracy. Naturally, this makes it a good idea. They're a clever bunch, those Urza's block archers.\n  \n   \nThen these dopes come along. \"They fletch their arrows with the feathers of angels.\" They also braid their scraggly beards and get lip piercings and make digeridoos out of PVC pipes. Yes, as of 7th edition, they are a band of dirty, no-good hippies who desecrate dead angels because they think it makes them cool. Without that note on accuracy, we have to come up with all of the conclusions by ourselves. Shame.",
      "posted_by": "Kirbster",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost143006\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">...why did the change the flavour text? The <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"5771\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=5771\">original version</a> at least mentioned <i>why</i> the arrows were fletched like so. It improved accuracy. Naturally, this makes it a good idea. They're a clever bunch, those Urza's block archers.\r<br/> <br/>Then these dopes come along. \"They fletch their arrows with the feathers of angels.\" They also braid their scraggly beards and get lip piercings and make digeridoos out of PVC pipes. Yes, as of 7th edition, they are a band of dirty, no-good hippies who desecrate dead angels because they think it makes them cool. Without that note on accuracy, we have to come up with all of the conclusions by ourselves. Shame.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '143006'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy37159\">Kirbster</span>\r\n                                (3/10/2011 5:31:09 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"floa