    {
      "id": "PopularPost128999",
      "post_content": "Agreed, that flavour doesn't seem very {W}.. (are they recycling dead angel feathers? That would seems more {B}{G} than anything.. or are they hunting angels..? That just doesn't seem white *at all*.  \n  \nAs for the mechanics of the card itself, instead of playing this, for {5}{W} you could instead get:  \n[Mirror-Sigil Sergeant](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirror-Sigil Sergeant) which can be devastating in the right deck.  \n[Auratouched Mage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Auratouched Mage), just run it with [Eldrazi Con\\*\\*\\*ion](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eldrazi Con***ion) and you have a 13/13 with trample and annihilator 2.   \n[Noble Templar](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Noble Templar) with 3 more toughness and vigilance, also has plainscycling.  \nNot to mention the swarm of better creature that have more {W} colour commitment, such as the often mentioned [Baneslayer Angel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Baneslayer Angel)  \n  \nThere are just better cards out there, the {T} ability is limited at best.",
      "posted_by": "tcollins",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost128999\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">Agreed, that flavour doesn't seem very {W}.. (are they recycling dead angel feathers? That would seems more {B}{G} than anything.. or are they hunting angels..? That just doesn't seem white <i>at all</i>.<br/><br/>As for the mechanics of the card itself, instead of playing this, for {5}{W} you could instead get:<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mirror-Sigil Sergeant\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirror-Sigil Sergeant\">Mirror-Sigil Sergeant</a> which can be devastating in the right deck.<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Auratouched Mage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Auratouched Mage\">Auratouched Mage</a>, just run it with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Eldrazi Con***ion\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eldrazi Con***ion\">Eldrazi Con***ion</a> and you have a 13/13 with trample and annihilator 2. <br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Noble Templar\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Noble Templar\">Noble Templar</a> with 3 more toughness and vigilance, also has plainscycling.<br/>Not to mention the swarm of better creature that have more {W} colour commitment, such as the often mentioned <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Baneslayer Angel\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Baneslayer Angel\">Baneslayer Angel</a><br/><br/>There are just better cards out there, the {T} ability is limited at best.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '128999'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy44184\">tcollins</span>\r\n                                (1/17/2011 12:23:25 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
